OL,5,G1900 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,6,     FBen ventures to the 'Emerald Isle'
OL,7,     Fto visit Georg and Bettina, an
OL,8,     Felderly European couple (from
OL,9,     FAustria and Germany) who made the
OL,10,     FIrish wilderness their home nearly
OL,11,     F40 years ago.
OL,12,G2000 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,13,     FBen Fogle ventures to the
OL,14,     Flesser-known Greek island of
OL,15,     FAndros to visit Sandy, founder of
OL,16,     Fa remote animal shelter perched on
OL,17,     Fthe slopes of the island's highest
OL,18,     Fpeak.
